{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1774933798.495662", "card_id": "Q_2021961267590513689", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 165}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高校多名贫困生兼职送外卖被处分，校方回应「中止处分流程未实际处罚」，这合理吗？处分流程为啥如此随意？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，重庆工信职业学院的林同学 (化姓) 称，因兼职配送校内学生外卖，自己收到了来自学校的违纪处分通知书，后处分流程又被校方中止。 涉事学校一名工作人员回应称，已与涉事学生沟通过，且已中止处分流程，并未对其进行实际处罚，事情已妥善解决。 陕西恒达律师事务所高级合伙人赵良善分析称，学生享有参加社会实践与勤工助学的合法权利，学校不得以概括性兜底条款随意限制学生劳动权，学校处分程序的启动、中止乃至终止均缺乏明确的成文法依据及书面说明。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8190d45899d5bde8c689e350decd3b11_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "467 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021961267590513689"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI87Lrq72T4uITEAMaCTExODk1NjgyNCCMuKjOBjAAOPwCQAByEzIwMjE5NjEyNjc1OTA1MTM2ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1774933798.496661", "card_id": "Q_2019342722851452166", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 508}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在豆包完全免费使用，那字节跳动开发豆包的意义是什么？如何盈利？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-a6a6a04fbab6067363b851c20c1a1815.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "395 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019342722851452166"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI87Lrq72T4uITEAMaCTExODg2MjI3MiDWqoLOBjAAOJUJQAFyEzIwMTkzNDI3MjI4NTE0NTIxNjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1774933798.498349", "card_id": "Q_2021910124273