。执飞机型为空客 320-271。川航飞尼泊尔的航班上有乘客在厕所吸烟！航司称已被警方带离 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d3d42f5743ac146bca6ccfdd739eff9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022009734304195595"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI87Lrq72T4uITEAMaCTExODk1OTAyOCCvkqnOBjAAONECQBtyEzIwMjIwMDk3MzQzMDQxOTU1OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1774933798.534701", "card_id": "Q_2022233810687854278", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "官方首提将制定「地方附加税法」，本次新税的设立目标是什么，万亿级预期规模对经济将有何积极意义？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "请各位从积极角度，客观分析此项新政： 中国一个新的税种：地方附加税正在加快推进。财政部披露 2025 年法治政府建设年度报告，在涉及 2026 年工作打算时，该报告首次提出做好地方附加税法等法律法规的制定、修订工作。这也是官方首次提出制定地方附加税法。官方首提制定地方附加税法 _ 腾讯新闻「地方附加税」改革将启，万亿级新税种如何设立 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022233810687854278"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI87Lrq72T4uITEAMaCTExODk2NDQwOSDfs6zOBjAAOBxAHHITMjAyMjIzMzgxMDY4Nzg1NDI3OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1774933798.535503", "card_id": "Q_2019058618901755317", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《三言二拍》杜十娘篇中的孙富会不会就是李甲的爹派过去的？"}, 